AB  - In the version of “The Economic Effects of a Borrower Bailout: Evidence from an Emerging Market” by Xavier Giné and Martin Kanz (10.1093/rfs/hhx073) that originally published online, two citations (Mian and Sufi, 2014 and Behn, Haselmann, et al. 2014) were not hyperlinked and a wording was incorrect in the reference Agarwal, S., et al. 2017.These errors have now been corrected online.
